        "version_id": "CNV",
        "version_name": "新譯本",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "所以，我們要藉著耶穌，常常把頌讚的祭品獻給　神，這就是承認他的名的人嘴唇的果子。"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "我們應當靠着耶穌，常常以頌讚為祭獻給神，這就是那承認主名之人嘴唇的果子。"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Through Him then, let us continually offer up a sacrifice of praise to God, that is, the fruit of lips that give thanks to His name."
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Through Jesus, therefore, let us continually offer to God a sacrifice of praise—the fruit of lips that openly profess his name."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Therefore, let us offer through Jesus a continual sacrifice of praise to God, proclaiming our allegiance to his name."
      }
